HEADWORD: Scintillant
<hw>Scin"til*lant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>scintillans</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>scintillare</ets> to sparkle. See
<er>Scintillate</er>.]</ety> <def>Emitting sparks, or fine igneous
particles; sparkling.</def> <rj><au>M. Green.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scintillate</ent>⟦br⟧
